            <br />
            Практика план:
            <div class="col-md-10">
                @Html.TextArea("praktikaPlan", "", new { id = "praktikaPlan", @class = "whatever-class", @cols = 20, @rows = 1,  autocomplete = "off" })
            </div>
            <br />
            Практика всего:
            <div class="col-md-10">
                @Html.TextArea("praktikaVsego", "", new { id = "praktikaVsego", @class = "whatever-class", @cols = 20, @rows = 1,  autocomplete = "off" })
            </div>
            <br />
            Лабораторные план:
